v0.43.0: distinct critter species

- new heritable 'species' gene (5 archetypes) drives body proportions, features, MOTION, and SMARTNESS:
  Pebble (round, big-eyed, slow), Foxling (sleek, pointy-eared, quick & clever), Hopkin (tall, springy hopper), Slink (long, low, earless slitherer), Beetlebug (wide, antennaed, skittery & dim)
- smarts multiplies sense range + steering finesse (clear survival differences); locomotion adds bob/hop/wobble per species
- inherited like clan; very rarely speciates on mutation; mixed via crossover; old saves default to Pebble
- follow panel shows the species name
